evolved Western cultures

00:39:49.090 --> 00:39:52.270
where it's considered
odd to eat insects.

00:39:52.270 --> 00:39:58.540
So again, potentially,
insects could

00:39:58.540 --> 00:40:03.670
be a great source of sustainable
food, sustainable protein.

00:40:03.670 --> 00:40:05.630
