exotic either.

00:40:08.590 --> 00:40:09.970
I have experimented
a little bit,

00:40:09.970 --> 00:40:11.830
but I'm only just
sort of starting

00:40:11.830 --> 00:40:13.009
to get my head around it.

00:40:13.009 --> 00:40:14.550
