00:40:30.887 --> 00:40:32.470
You've got these
little black beetles,

00:40:32.470 --> 00:40:35.557
and they produce these
wriggly little mealworms.

00:40:35.557 --> 00:40:37.390
I don't know if anyone's
familiar with them.

00:40:37.390 --> 00:40:38.920
