food very, very seriously.

00:43:32.860 --> 00:43:35.430
And I think putting it at
the center of a celebration

00:43:35.430 --> 00:43:37.770
is absolutely no problem.

00:43:37.770 --> 00:43:41.340
I went to my goddaughter's
21st-birthday party

00:43:41.340 --> 00:43:42.870
last weekend.

00:43:42.870 --> 00:43:45.000
And she decided to have
a vegetarian feast,

00:43:45.000 --> 00:43:46.960
and it was absolutely delicious.

00:43:46.960 --> 00:43:48.345
So yeah, lots you can do.

00:43:48.345 --> 00:43:50.220
And don't let your
friends talk you out of it

00:43:50.220 --> 00:43:51.770
if that's the way
you want to go.

