00:44:29.439 --> 00:44:29.980
AUDIENCE: Hi.

00:44:29.980 --> 00:44:30.480
I'm Neri.

00:44:30.480 --> 00:44:31.510
Thank you so much for your talk.

00:44:31.510 --> 00:44:33.120
It was really,
